cern.colt.list.adapter

Class ObjectListAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList
        • cern.colt.list.adapter.ObjectListAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable, java.util.Collection, java.util.List

    public class ObjectListAdapter
extends java.util.AbstractList
implements java.util.List
    Adapter that permits an ObjectArrayList to be viewed and treated as a JDK 1.2 AbstractList. Makes the contained list compatible with the JDK 1.2 Collections Framework.
